step-1
Add allpurposeflour,cocopowder,bakingsoda,saltand stirit well.
Take a new bowl and add butter,sugar beat until it become smooth.
After beating it add 2eggs and stir it well add vegetable oil
beat until combined pour 1cup ou buttermilk again beat until combined.
Add flour vanila extract,red food coloring stir it well pour it into a baking bowl bake it for 40minutes
cool the cake for 10 minutes.
step-2
Cut the cake into two parts and apply the cream.Then the cake will be ready.
